sentences.english: This is a very good Huffman tree C code can run.
sentences.chinese: 這是一個很不錯的赫夫曼樹C代碼，可以運行。

sentences.english: Tis the god Hercules, whom Antony loved, Now leaves him.
sentences.chinese: 這是安東尼所崇拜的赫剌克勒斯，現在離開他了。

sentences.english: So they will call their bible Tanakh often,or just the bible.
sentences.chinese: 所以他們通常叫聖經爲塔納赫。

sentences.english: Former Central Bank Governor Ahmed Ould Daddah was third with less than 14 percent.
sentences.chinese: 前中央銀行行長達達赫得票不到14%，位居第三。

sentences.english: Mr. Darcy said very little, and Mr. Hurst nothing at all.
sentences.chinese: 達西先生說話不多，赫斯脫先生完全一言不發。

sentences.english: With the support of al-Adid, Shirkuh entered Cairo unopposed.
sentences.chinese: 在阿迪德的支持下，謝爾庫赫無阻地進入了開羅。

sentences.english: Judge Hoffman sentenced the seven men to prison.
sentences.chinese: 赫夫曼法官對那七個人宣判入獄。

sentences.english: Hermes immediately obeyed and glided down from the heavens to the earth.
sentences.chinese: 赫密斯立刻遵命，從天上飛到地面上。

sentences.english: It will be his 14th of the campaign, one more than Petr Cech and Brad Friedel.
sentences.chinese: 這是他的第14場戰役，比切赫和弗裏德爾領先一場。

sentences.english: Hermes hoped that the music would put Argus to sleep, but it didn't.
sentences.chinese: 赫密斯希望音樂能讓阿格斯入眠，但他並未睡着。

sentences.english: Atlas got the golden apples for Hercules because he wanted to be the king himself.
sentences.chinese: 阿特拉斯爲赫克斯得到金蘋果，因爲他自己想做國王。

sentences.english: Doctor Hviesten says his pulse is elevated.
sentences.chinese: 赫維斯騰大夫說他的脈博加快了。

sentences.english: Hurst looked at her with astonishment.
sentences.chinese: 赫斯脫先生驚奇地朝她望了一下。

sentences.english: In the Hebrides they shear their sheep later than anywhere else.
sentences.chinese: 在赫伯里茲，剪羊毛的時間比其他任何地方都要晚。

sentences.english: Investigation report is released, Defense Minister Keli He announced his resignation.
sentences.chinese: 調查報告公佈後，國防部長克利赫宣佈辭職。

sentences.english: However, the owners of the dogs were very glad that Herriot would help their pets.
sentences.chinese: 但是狗的主人們非常高興，赫瑞爾幫助了他們的寵物。
